OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F305A1774944309
OL,3,CRecord number of checks on water
OL,4,Ccompany assets reveals thousands of
OL,5,Cbreaches
OL,7,FRegulators have uncovered thousands of
OL,8,Fbreaches of environmental rules by
OL,9,Fwater companies, as teams say they
OL,10,Fcarried out a record number of
OL,11,Finspections in the past year.
OL,13,FThe Environment Agency (EA) said it
OL,14,Fhad expanded its inspections of
OL,15,Ftreatment works, sewage pumping
OL,16,Fstations and storm overflows,
OL,17,Fcompleting more than 10,000 checks of
OL,18,Fwater company assets in the past year.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G1/11
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,306,300,200,140,000,100
PN,30502
SC,0002
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F305A1774944309
OL,3,CRecord number of checks on water
OL,4,Ccompany assets reveals thousands of
OL,5,Cbreaches
OL,7,FInspection teams uncovered more than
OL,8,F3,000 permit condition breaches, where
OL,9,Fcompanies are failing to comply with
OL,10,Fenvironmental legislation.
OL,12,FThis led to demands for improvements
OL,13,Fissued to water companies, including
OL,14,Frepairing sewage works and upgrading
OL,15,Finfrastructure, the EA said.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G2/11
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,306,300,200,140,000,100
PN,30503
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F305A1774944309
OL,3,CRecord number of checks on water
OL,4,Ccompany assets reveals thousands of
OL,5,Cbreaches
OL,7,FThe agency said permit conditions
OL,8,Fcould be breached for a number of
OL,9,Freasons, such as equipment failure,
OL,10,Feffluent not meeting water quality
OL,11,Fstandards, not treating the required
OL,12,Famount of wastewater or failing to
OL,13,Fmanage the water and sewage network in
OL,14,Fline with permit requirements.
OL,16,FIt comes as more funding and 500
OL,17,Fadditional staff have allowed the
OL,18,Fagency to undertake far more
OL,19,Finspections, up from 4,600 in 2024/
OL,20,F2025 to more than 10,000 this
OL,21,Ffinancial year.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G3/11
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,306,300,200,140,000,100
PN,30504
SC,0004
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F305A1774944309
OL,3,CRecord number of checks on water
OL,4,Ccompany assets reveals thousands of
OL,5,Cbreaches
OL,7,FAnd the EA suggests its greater
OL,8,Fscrutiny of water companies is having
OL,9,Fan effect on making them manage their
OL,10,Fassets more responsibly, with 22% of
OL,11,Fsite visits uncovering at least one
OL,12,Fissue this year ` down from 25% the
OL,13,Fprevious year.
OL,15,FHelen Wakeham, director for water at
OL,16,Fthe Environment Agency, said: "In our
OL,17,Frole as regulators of the water
OL,18,Findustry, we are changing how we
OL,19,Foperate ` with better data, record
OL,20,Flevels of new staff and greater powers
OL,21,Fto do our job effectively.
OL,26,@xD@_OU
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G4/11
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,306,300,200,140,000,100
PN,30505
SC,0005
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F305A1774944309
OL,3,CRecord number of checks on water
OL,4,Ccompany assets reveals thousands of
OL,5,Cbreaches
OL,7,F"Inspections are a vital preventative
OL,8,Fmeasure, with our teams issuing over
OL,9,F3,000 individual actions to water
OL,10,Fcompanies, including repairing sewage
OL,11,Fworks and upgrading infrastructure.
OL,13,F"Together, this will drive meaningful
OL,14,Fimprovements in performance, hold
OL,15,Fpersistent offenders to account and
OL,16,Fultimately create a cleaner water
OL,17,Fenvironment."
OL,26,@oD@AOUuD@AOUyD@MO]
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G5/11
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,306,300,200,140,000,100
PN,30506
SC,0006
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F305A1774944309
OL,3,CRecord number of checks on water
OL,4,Ccompany assets reveals thousands of
OL,5,Cbreaches
OL,7,FWater minister Emma Hardy added:
OL,8,F"Thanks to our investment in the
OL,9,FEnvironment Agency, inspectors are out
OL,10,Fin force, checking water company
OL,11,Fassets at unprecedented levels and
OL,12,Ftaking action where standards aren't
OL,13,Fmet.
OL,15,F"This greater oversight of water
OL,16,Fcompanies coupled with our long-term
OL,17,Freforms will prevent problems before
OL,18,Fthey occur and ensure serial offenders
OL,19,Fare punished, ensuring a healthy,
OL,20,Fsustainable water system for the
OL,21,Ffuture."
OL,26,@pD@AOUwD@AOU}D@HO]
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G6/11
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,306,300,200,140,000,100
PN,30507
SC,0007
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F305A1774944309
OL,3,CRecord number of checks on water
OL,4,Ccompany assets reveals thousands of
OL,5,Cbreaches
OL,7,FHowever, campaigners say more needs to
OL,8,Fbe done.
OL,10,FJames Wallace, chief executive of
OL,11,FRiver Action, said water companies had
OL,12,Fdischarged more than 1.8 million hours
OL,13,Fof sewage into rivers, lakes and seas
OL,14,Fin 2025, while most of England's 35
OL,15,Finland bathing sites were unsafe for
OL,16,Fswimming.
OL,18,F"It is good to see the government
OL,19,Fgetting serious about water quality,
OL,20,Fbut inspections alone will not fix the
OL,21,Fproblem.
OL,26,@zD@AOU
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G7/11
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,306,300,200,140,000,100
PN,30508
SC,0008
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F305A1774944309
OL,3,CRecord number of checks on water
OL,4,Ccompany assets reveals thousands of
OL,5,Cbreaches
OL,7,F"With prosecutions taking years to
OL,8,Freach court and fines far too low,
OL,9,Fwater polluters are not being properly
OL,10,Fheld to account.
OL,12,F"The upcoming Water Reform Bill is a
OL,13,Fonce-in-a-generation opportunity to
OL,14,Freset the system.
OL,16,F"The government must take back control
OL,17,Fof water company ownership and ensure
OL,18,Fbill payers' money cleans up rivers,
OL,19,Fnot investor pockets," he urged.
OL,26,@oD@AOUtD@AOUxD@AOU{D@VO]
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G8/11
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,306,300,200,140,000,100
PN,30509
SC,0009
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F305A1774944309
OL,3,CRecord number of checks on water
OL,4,Ccompany assets reveals thousands of
OL,5,Cbreaches
OL,7,FRichard Benwell, chief executive of
OL,8,Fenvironmental coalition Wildlife and
OL,9,FCountryside Link, said: "It's good
OL,10,Fthat inspection numbers have doubled,
OL,11,Fbut the scale of lawbreaking is
OL,12,Falarming.
OL,14,F"Thousands of breaches in a single
OL,15,Fyear show that pollution is business
OL,16,Fas usual for water companies."
OL,26,@qD@YOUvD@AOUxD@^O]
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G9/11
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,306,300,200,140,000,100
PN,30510
SC,0010
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F305A1774944309
OL,3,CRecord number of checks on water
OL,4,Ccompany assets reveals thousands of
OL,5,Cbreaches
OL,7,FHe warned that enforcement remained
OL,8,Ftoo slow and weak and said: "When the
OL,9,Fnew water regulator is set up, it must
OL,10,Fbe empowered to act decisively `
OL,11,Finspecting more assets, including the
OL,12,Fcondition of nature on company land,
OL,13,Fand handing down rapid, significant
OL,14,Fpenalties, including criminal
OL,15,Fsanctions where needed."
OL,26,@pD@]OUwD@XO]
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                   G10/11
